sentences: Marco Álvarez Gutierrez (born November 5, 1972) is a Spanish musician.
Born in Gijon, when he was almost 14 years old discovered his passion for heavy metal.
He has also been the drummer for Stormy Mondays and Heavy metal/progressive metal band called Avalanch along with Alberto Rionda until the band hiatus in 2012.
